													<img role="presentation" src="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2018/07/07/universal/es/07Caparros-ES-1/merlin_140923245_425b3b87-d2df-401e-b898-122b5897dc5e-mediumThreeByTwo210.jpg" alt="El mundo Mundial 26: Sarah" itemprop="thumbnailUrl" />
								
								
